Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've surpassed the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:42.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Ho! Steer that rudder! Hard to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.92,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Ho! Our high-flyin' lives are every which way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:58.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When the sun goes down, there's a bon voyage bash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:04.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't sad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:11.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're alive, we'll meet again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:15.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast straight through a headwind, set off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong until the tears dry up! A man gotta be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:25.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, friends, laugh one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:29.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of our strong, strong bonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:37.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, grab that map to the shining future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't any of you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems okay to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After using all that magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the members of the guild and the \Npeople of the city are safe as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single person has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That shouldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Fairy Law was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your heart, Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:54.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You inherited more than just the \Nmaster's strength and magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You also got a heart that feels for your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:02.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law only affects those \Nthe caster sees as his enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what this means, right Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings he has deep down \Nare revealed through his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic never lies, Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who gets in my way is my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just quit this already, Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a crap about that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am me! Not just some old man's "grandson!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so puffed up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does being Gramps' grandson make\Nyou so different from the rest of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screaming about blood relatives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody in the guild is in the same family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't know! Aren't \Nwe guildmates anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us know! That's why \Nwe help each other out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear off the face of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the guild dies, it'll never be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's our home to return to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even die right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think you could beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild isn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about it, Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:10.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakdown Fist of the Thunder Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:22.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100 years too early for you \Nto be preaching to me, pipsqueak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can still stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damned brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure there's not even a trace left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use that magic while \NNatsu is like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Halberd of the Thunder Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron... Did he use himself \Nas a lightning rod?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flaming Elbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic will shatter a dragon's \Nscales, crush its innards,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and cut down its very soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True dragon-killing attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blazing Flashover Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you come, Grandeenay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:40.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought coming here or \Nmeddling were forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That child really goes overboard, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who he takes after?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But his luck won't last him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not interfere with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:03.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to anger me? Anger Igneel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. No matter how we may be worried, \Nthere is not a thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is believe \Nin the power of the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is... Never mind, let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:25.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Fantasia's been postponed \Nuntil tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does their master not feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be retiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who the next master will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That problem-child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sorta makes you think, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I known him since he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we all get older, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Poluchka, it seems his \Nlife has been saved for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not. The master is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! I didn't know what was \Ngoing to happen for a little while there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man isn't gonna \Nkick the bucket so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the master is quite old. Stressing his \Nheart more will only make his health worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But are we really doing the \NFantasia under these conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:21.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what the master wants. It's precisely \Nat times like this that we should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is also looking forward \Nto seeing the Fantasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Juvia just joined...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she troubled or happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we do have a lot of injured people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rule is: anyone who can \Nstill move has to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll participate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy about it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those guys \Ncan't participate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's anything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance. No way you \Ncan participate, trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he can understand him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously doubt it's anything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes your cold-hearted \Nfeelings scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:27.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this, we've fixed one \Nof the problems in the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you hang your head, \Nyou think we'll let you see the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cease this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the inside clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:54.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some interpretation, if you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time was two against \None, so I ain't satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:37.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna lose next time. \NI'll fight you anytime, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought he won?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call that winning either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:52.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was in the war with \NPhantom, it gives me chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's time for everyone \Nto get ready for the Fantasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know I'm in \Nit, we'd better practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will do her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look me in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guilds, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a place where friends gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a place where you can get work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And to kids with no place \Nto go, they can be a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not something you can own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:57.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild is the confidence and \Ngood will of each individual,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and from them the tough \Nbonds that are formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:07.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You went against that good will and \Nthreatened the lives of your fellow members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not something that can be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... wanted to make this guild... stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:29.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try relaxing a little, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, maybe you'd see \Nthings you can't right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd hear words that you can't hear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising you was like a \Nnew lease on life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need power. You \Ndon't have to be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be happy and healthy. That's \Nall I ever wanted for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Sorry for the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you the only one that's expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we just as guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what the old man decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Can't you just say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to take all the \Nresponsibility on yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:20.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I don't have any \Nattachments left to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Natsu and Gray will \Nbe against your expulsion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what they say, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! What'll \Nhappen to the Raijin Tribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent, Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened to Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pitiful man... He thought he was \Nusing you, but in fact he was being used himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For 8 years, he never noticed I was \Npretending to be the spirit of Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brainwashing made \Nthe plan work perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:33.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The upheaval in the Council \Nand the firing of Etherion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went exactly to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:41.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. While Jellal was on his rampage, \Nyou could move as you pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, we've obtained one of \Nthe keys needed to unlock the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Master Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this... Jellal-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:30.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Mr. Shooby doo Bop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:38.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Ivan, your son. \NI found out where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about giving you such a dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No screw ups here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:47.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no idea I'm a double agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let him do as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too fancy for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more funky than fancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop those freaky movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, aren't you going to participate \Nin the Fantasia this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your big moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching from the stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be able \Nto see where you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in the middle of the parade...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:38.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that even if I can't see where you \Nare, I'm always looking at you, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:33.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't see you... Even if \Nwe are separated far apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch over you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's way more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Fairy Tail wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still just a rookie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got to work hard and become \Na wizard that won't lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:13.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, they say smiling weird \Nlike that'll give you wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just theoretically. So touchy, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, we finally had a \Nnice moment there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:24.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}this{\i0} is how they end it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:33.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:43.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,we even kindly overlooked the little lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:58.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll protect that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:03.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:10.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:15.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,all my happiness and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:23.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:30.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it like we've just been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:36.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like flowers blown in a summer wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:44.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,let us bloom brightly in this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:24:00.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I heard that a reporter from the Weekly \NSorcerer is going to come interview Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! You mean that magazine that's \Nalways printin' bad stuff about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smack 'em good!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:08.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think it was all the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, don't hurt them, \Nno matter what, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.63,0:24:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Day of Fated Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? They call that a "flag".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:21.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't get your hopes up, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
